Featured Projects

Michigan Covid-19 Dashboard

Worked as a project manager, recruiter, and software tester to create a Covid-19 dashboard for the Michigan Governors office. Collaborated with students, professors and admins from the University of Michigan; School of Information, School of Public Health, Art and Design, College of Engineering, Jackson Health, Google, McKinsey and Co., and Ford Motor Company.

dashboard government link project funding in the news
